| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2364 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2f9249c0-29fd-508d-a25c-3e7951cc5172"
